1. Userdata can be used for any customization at launch.

   a) You can install any software

   b) Prepare the instance to join a cluster like consul cluster, ECS cluster (docker orchestration).

   c) Execute commands or scripts

   d) Mount volumes

2. Userdata is only excuted during the creation of the instance, not when the instance reboots

3. Terraform allows you to add userdata to the aws_instance resource.

   a) Just as a string for simple commands

   b) Using templates (for more complex instructions)
